snippet: The Jets say they want to move beyond last season’s disappointment, but the receiver has been averse to publicly acknowledging any culpability in their demise in 2011.
abstract: New York Jets reconvene for the first time their 2011 season collapsed in dysfunction; players say they want to move beyond last season’s disappointment, but receiver Santonio Holmes, the symbol of the Jets lockerroom turmoil, has been averse to publicly acknowledging any culpability in their demise in 2011.
lead_paragraph: The Jets say they want to move beyond last season’s disappointment, but the receiver has been averse to publicly acknowledging any culpability in their demise in 2011.

headline.seo: As Jets Regroup, Santonio Holmes Has No Regrets
